          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "4. Performance Optimization and Monitoring"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Monitor API latency and error rates using tools like Prometheus. Implement caching for frequently used voice designs to reduce API calls. Scale horizontally by distributing requests across multiple API keys if needed. Regularly update client libraries to incorporate performance improvements from model updates."
